---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us - What to Watch Today" description="Learn more about the team behind What to Watch Today and our mission.">
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 pt-20 pb-16">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-indigo-500 mb-4 text-center">About Us</h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-slate-700 mb-8 text-center">
      “What to Watch Today” was born from a question we all ask ourselves: *"What should we watch now?"*
    </p>
    <br />

    <div class="space-y-6 text-slate-700 text-base leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        Our mission is to help you find the perfect movie or series for any mood or moment. We know how much time gets lost scrolling through endless options—and we’re here to help you get that time back.
      </p>
      <p>
        Every recommendation you find here is curated to give you a night that’s relaxing, exciting, or just plain fun—without the frustration of decision fatigue.
      </p>
      <p>
        Whether you're watching with a partner, friends, family, or flying solo, What to Watch Today is your go-to source for inspiration.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
